                        <provenance>
                            <p>The volume belonged to the Franciscan convent in <placeName ref="https://www.manuscripta.se/place/100364">Orléans</placeName>, according to a note on <locus from="L1v" to="L1v" scheme="folios"/>.</p>
                        </provenance>
                        <provenance>
                            <p>In Jaches’s catalogue of 1698 (U 122), p. 304, listed as <quote>236</quote> and <quote>200</quote>. In the catalogue of 1734 (U 125e), p. 12, listed as <quote>no 6</quote>.</p>
                        </provenance>
