                                                <citedRange from="11090" to="11090" unit="number"/>
                                            </bibl>: <locus from="59r" to="59r" scheme="folios"/> (line 1): <quote>Numquid capies leena predam Leena est ecclesia</quote> (Job 38:39); <locus from="59v" to="59v" scheme="folios"/> (line 24): <quote>Numquid fiduciam In rhinocerotis fortitudine</quote> (Job 39:11); <locus from="61r" to="61r" scheme="folios"/> (line 1): <quote>Super quo bases illius [...] Terre huius bases sancte ecclesie</quote> (Job 38:6); <locus from="61v" to="61v" scheme="folios"/> (line 31): <quote>Sciebas tunc quod nasciturus esses [...] Ac si diceret aperte</quote> (Job 38:21).</p>
